phrases: Wow, it is old school superhero shading!
I like the color of your hair.
It looks like a blue crystal.
Make a contract with me and become a member of Pied Piper!
Do not talk to me before the playback ends.
But why does it look like that?
It is cool, is not it?
It is built from stuff found inside the Scub Coral.

I would like to talk to you.

We will be doing it over here.
Sorry for making you wait, Ao.
I will get someone to look for him.
Do not tell me you guys snuck on in Okinawa?
It matches the data Fleur gathered.
But there is one point where his genome map is very different from ours.
Especially the positions of his optic nerves.
His range of perception might be much wider.
He may be able to see electromagnetic waves beyond human limits, such as infrared or ultraviolet light.
Then this world might look very different to him.
I wonder what they are talking about...
You are a perfectly normal twelve year old.
It is a part of you, and something that you inherited from your mother.
A few thousand people work here at the Swiss HQ.
We are at the top of the tower now, the base of the IFO teams.
The tower continues underground as well.
I think all together it is about the size of a city.
Ahead of here are our quarters.
He is the newbie we just recruited.
He has an ID already, I assume?
Whoops, I forgot to ask the Chief!
Come on, it does not really matter!
Moments ago, a peculiar intruder was spotted at headquarters.
We assume it is a sloth.
So far, it has escaped capture.
If something happened to him, Naru would get mad at me!
Is that girl on the island your girlfriend?
Anyway, I have to look for him!
I am the president of Generation Bleu, Christophe Blanc.
Do you have something interesting for me?
When your IFOs took something out of the Scub,
it turned gray and the bursts calmed down.
So this is how you do your hyper-rescues?
No one knows this little secret, I guess.
Our company focuses on studying the Scub Coral.
There is nothing weird about this.
I have seen that kind of shiny thing before.
I got something like that planted on my FP,
but then some Scub appeared from it, and bursted.
Is your company really an innocent volunteer organization as you portray yourselves to be?
They are Goldilocks, another IFO team just like us.
Is not the Fukai kid with you?
Do not say it like that!
We will be colleagues from now on!
The president has a screw loose.
I heard you entered the Zone and defeated a Secret.
I did not know that still worked!
Are you going to eat all that?
You did not tell her she is tiny.
You may be on the ace team, but we are still your superiors!
You have got cream on your nose.
Anyway, nice to meet you, Ao.
If you have got any questions about life here, feel free to ask.
but the Generation Bleu's fluffy mascot is obviously Bruno!
Pied Piper guys cannot have any!
I could live without it too...
But you should go back home right now.
If you stay here, you would upset those who care about you.
The order was for Goldilocks, not Pied Piper.
However, there is a mid-sized hurricane closing in on the location.
These guys are Pippo and Han.
It is the duty of us elders to give the young ones a chance.
I do not like to involve civilians on a whim.
The Medon is now in suborbital flight.
I do not have my ID yet.
Are you sure this is okay?
He said I would make people dear to me sad.
When did you two become best friends?
Ao, why did you come here?
This is a very rare case.
There are plenty of examples where it took a while for the Secret to emerge.
Do not let your guard down!
Then should not we just collect the Quartz now?
Girls, do not go too far ahead.
If there is any danger, we will contain it.
Maev and I always keep an eye out for Chloe.
My body is small and I am just 11 years old,
but I am not a kid anymore!
What are the Allied Forces doing here?
It is on the radar, but there is no response!
The Secrets were hiding inside the hurricane?!
The seawater, lifted by the Secret's high velocity rotation, prevented visual detection.
It is currently within a 100km radius off the coast of Punta Gallinas.
Just to make sure, Pied Piper is to prepare for mobilization!
The children just returned from action!
So in this case, Kyrie could stand by above the clouds...
You think you are going to fly with us?
They just wanted to get the Mark I.
It is the old fart president after all.
That is the way he thinks.
Ao, what have you come here for?
Requiem, Gloria, Credo... none of them are responding.
We are now going to start rescue operations.
Team Pied Piper, hurry with your preparations!
Where do you think you are going?
That is yours and yours only.
The left arm works fine as well.
Is not it called the Mark I?
As per the president's orders, the craft is registered under the name Nirvash.
Should not you say something to him?
He joined us on his own.
There is no need for that.
Triton: start engines and prepare for launch.
Moving the Triton to the catapult.
Setting the Triton onto the catapult.
We have got clearance from control.
Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Lacking any certainty, Ao sets out on a journey with Nirvash.
Beyond the dark clouds that hide a dreadful sight,
a ray of light gives birth to the shadow of a seeker of truth.
Eureka Seven AO, episode six: Light My Fire.
Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
